in marketing and visual design.\n* **Mohamed Bassem Mazghouni** (software developer), hold BS degree in software development. He hold 2 years of experience in game development.\n![](https://www.amalxr.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/quotes.svg)\n#### “ WE ARE DEMOCRATIZING VIRTUAL REHABILITATION ”\n© 2025 All rights reserved [**AMAL XR**](https://www.amalxr.com/about/)",
